fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.codegen

Interface TypedElement

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Assignable, Expression
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalVariable, MethodParameterGenerator, OptionalGenerator, RequestGenerator, SimpleField, TypeAdaptorGenerator

    public interface TypedElement
    A Java source code element that has a type. Typed elements have a fixed type at runtime. All Expressions and Assignables are TypedElements.
